{"tid":98802,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"四月去北九州，行程求狠批","createTime":"2017-01-28T16:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T10:48:38.000Z","uid":37851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40c5b57bb9b79f179f0f23d05a892b25771a13d5","tid":98802,"uid":37851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"黎緊四月尾去, 想大家比下意見 <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 . 中午12點到, 住福岡<br />\n　　　 太宰府+柳川<br />\nDay 2 住福岡<br />\n　　　 行outlet<br />\nDay 3 住大分<br />\n　　　 去阿蘇山<br />\nDay 4 大分<br />\n　　　 昭和之町+真玉海岸日落/ 原尻瀑布<br />\nDay 5 由布院 <br />\n　　　 1泊2食<br />\nDay 6 福岡<br />\n　　　 中午返福岡 <br />\n　　　 之後行 天神地下街+博多運河城 +室內棒球機<br />\nDay 7 福岡<br />\n　　　 門司港+小倉<br />\nDay 8, 5點機走<br />\n　　　 Hea shopping + 執行李<br />\n<br />\n買5 day pass, day 34567用<br />\n<br />\n個行程OK嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下阿蘇值唔值得去？<br />\n因為由大分去阿蘇都要成3個幾鐘<br />\n阿蘇d交通又好似唔係好密<br />\n之前睇個遊記話去草千里<br />\n架車滿左人搞到要等下一班車　<br />\n但遊記話一班車相隔成個幾鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係抽走阿蘇轉去軍艦島好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34996784230dbe4228928cb09c40fdaa336c5b21","tid":98802,"uid":37851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9674327a7c1164f619db055ee60838cf104b870","tid":98802,"uid":37851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7fcf47c8d4022a5700917e981710cf6e781d54","tid":98802,"uid":50909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"我二月尾去 原本都諗住去阿蘇 但早幾個月又爆過 好多都封左 去黎都冇咩野玩同睇<br />\n<br />\n我有兩日去廣島玩"},{"pid":"4dd041bc9a359312aecec9b5c43ebba04c9834e1","tid":98802,"uid":80274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:45:09.000Z","msg":